    <a href="https://techcabal.com" target="_blank" class="tc-brand">TechCabal <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a>
